title: All Aboard - 24 Original All-Time Children's Favourites
description:
Well first off i'd like to personally thank DroGG for uploading the Nero disc image of this disc, as i used to have the cassette when i was little, i remember playing it until it chewed up, and i only recently remembered the album name, and DroGG was unsure about possibly hosting the mp3 version of the album. So i took it upon myself to upload it.

Secondly, please no bitching about the 128kbps bit-rate. 

Dont forget to support the artist, and buy or pre-order the album if you like it!.
I will seed to a ratio of 0:10, after that it is up to you to seed and keep the torrent alive.

Please Enjoy!
